<h1>New Message</h1>

<p>This app will send a text message to any valid US phone number.</br>
  Well, one day it will.  For now, James is using a <a href="https://www.twilio.com">Twilio</a> trial account, </br>
  so can only send to numbers that have been verified.</p>

<p>If you have a verified number, enter that, 10-digit phone number below,</br>
 and a message and you should receive that message on your phone in a few </br>
 seconds.</p>

<%= form_for :message, url: messages_path do |f| %>
  <p>
    <%= f.label :number_to_send_to %><br>
    <%= f.text_field :number_to_send_to %>
  </p>
 
  <p>
    <%= f.label :message_to_send %><br>
    <%= f.text_area :message_to_send %>
  </p>
 
  <p>
    <%= f.submit "Send My Message!" %>
  </p>
<% end %>